@startuml uc-13
autonumber
skinparam maxMessageSize 150
skinparam ParticipantPadding 20
skinparam BoxPadding 10

actor "User (Student/Staff)" as User

box "Presentation Layer" #LightCyan
participant "loginUI : LoginUI" as LoginUI
participant "ui : ForgotPasswordUI" as UI
end box

box "Business Logic Layer" #LightYellow
participant "authService : AuthenticationService" as AuthService
participant "emailManager : EmailNotificationManager" as EmailService
end box

box "Data Access Layer" #LightGreen
participant "userRecord : User" as UserDB
participant "tokenRecord : AuthToken" as TokenDB
end box

box "External Systems" #LightGray
participant "Email API Service" as EmailAPI
end box

== Initiation ==
User -> LoginUI: Select "Şifremi Unuttum" (Forgot Password)
activate LoginUI
LoginUI -> UI: Route to Reset Process
deactivate LoginUI

activate UI
UI --> User: displayResetForm() (Prompt for Email)

User -> UI: Enter registered email & Click "Sıfırlama Bağlantısı Gönder"
UI -> AuthService: initiatePasswordReset(email)
activate AuthService

AuthService -> UserDB: Check if email exists
activate UserDB
UserDB --> AuthService: Return match result
deactivate UserDB

alt Account not found (Alternative 4.a)
    AuthService --> UI: Error (User not found)
    UI --> User: Display error (Suggest re-enter or contact support)
else Account exists
    AuthService -> TokenDB: Create AuthToken (reset token, expiryDate)
    activate TokenDB
    TokenDB --> AuthService: Token generated
    deactivate TokenDB

    AuthService -> EmailService: sendStatusUpdate(email, resetLink)
    activate EmailService

    EmailService -> EmailAPI: Send email with reset link/code
    activate EmailAPI
    EmailAPI --> EmailService: Delivery Success
    deactivate EmailAPI

    EmailService --> AuthService: Confirmation
    deactivate EmailService

    AuthService --> UI: Reset link sent
    UI --> User: Display confirmation message
end
deactivate AuthService

== Password Reset Execution ==
User -> UI: Opens reset link from email / enters code
UI -> AuthService: Verify AuthToken validity
activate AuthService

AuthService -> TokenDB: Query token status and expiryDate
activate TokenDB
TokenDB --> AuthService: Return token data
deactivate TokenDB

alt Verification code expired or invalid (Alternative 6.b)
    AuthService --> UI: Invalid Token Error
    UI --> User: Prompt to request a new code
    
    opt User requests new code (Alternative 6.a)
        User -> UI: Request new link
        UI -> AuthService: initiatePasswordReset(email)
        note right: Flow repeats from token generation
    end
    
else Token valid
    AuthService --> UI: Token verified
    UI --> User: displayResetForm() (Prompt for New Password)

    User -> UI: Enter new password and confirm
    UI -> AuthService: validate & updatePassword(newPassword)

    alt Password does not meet security requirements (Alternative 8.a)
        AuthService --> UI: Validation Error (Fails policy)
        UI --> User: showPasswordRequirements()
        note right: User re-enters valid password
        
    else Valid Password
        AuthService -> UserDB: Update passwordHash
        activate UserDB
        UserDB --> AuthService: Update successful
        deactivate UserDB

        AuthService -> TokenDB: Invalidate AuthToken (isValid = false)
        activate TokenDB
        TokenDB --> AuthService: Token invalidated
        deactivate TokenDB

        AuthService --> UI: Password update successful
        UI --> User: Notify success and redirect to Login
    end
end

opt Cancellation of Password Reset (Alternative 3.a)
    User -> UI: Click "İptal" (Cancel)
    UI --> User: Discard changes & Return to LoginUI
end

deactivate AuthService
deactivate UI

@enduml